text: Dhugumatti isin kophaa taatanii akkuma yeroo jalqabaa isin uumnetti Wantoota Nuti isiniif kennine hunda dugda duuba keessanitti dhiiftanii gara keenya dhuftaniittuNuti manguddoota (taabota) keessan kan isin “kun warra Rabbiin waliin gabbarru” jedhaa turtan isin wajjiin hin arginu(Hariiroon) gidduu keessanii dhugumatti citeeraWanti isin mormaa turtanis isin jalaa badeera
